25|$|November 1997 - Former Houston Police Chief Lee P. Brown {{is elected}} as Houston's first African-American mayor; {{at the same}} time, Annise Parker is the first openly <b>gay</b> <b>or</b> <b>lesbian</b> city council member.|$|E
